            "title": "盤中速報 - 龍巖(5530)大跌7.04%，報81.9元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>龍巖(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5530:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5530\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5530-TW</a>)21日09:46股價下跌6.2元，報81.9元，跌幅7.04%，成交4,583張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>龍巖(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5530:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5530\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5530-TW</a>)所屬產業為其他業，主要業務為殯葬業。建設業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲22.36%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.07%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,146 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,097 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+49 張</li> <li>融資增減：+696 張</li> <li>融券增減：-67 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
